# TypeScript (NXTCM-components)

- Use TypeScript for new React components and utility/helper functions
- Avoid the `any` type; prefer `unknown` when the type is not known
- Add explicit return types to functions
- Use proper TypeScript error types instead of generic Error objects
- Type custom hooks with proper return types
- Type callback functions explicitly
